statements: SELECT student_id, program_name, intervention_date, effectiveness_score FROM evaluation_data;
SELECT * FROM evaluation_data WHERE student_id = 123;
SELECT program_name, intervention_date, effectiveness_score FROM evaluation_data WHERE intervention_id = 456;
SELECT student_id, intervention_id, program_name FROM evaluation_data ORDER BY effectiveness_score DESC;
SELECT * FROM evaluation_data WHERE intervention_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM evaluation_data WHERE student_id = 1;
SELECT program_name, intervention_date FROM evaluation_data WHERE intervention_id = 3 ORDER BY intervention_date DESC;
SELECT student_id, program_name, effectiveness_score FROM evaluation_data WHERE intervention_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31' ORDER BY effectiveness_score DESC;
SELECT intervention_id, AVG(effectiveness_score) AS avg_score FROM evaluation_data GROUP BY intervention_id HAVING avg_score > 7;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT student_id) AS total_students, AVG(effectiveness_score) AS avg_score FROM evaluation_data;
SELECT * FROM Evaluation;
SELECT student_name, effectiveness_rating FROM Evaluation WHERE intervention_type = 'Math';
SELECT program_name, completion_status FROM ProgramData WHERE start_date < '2022-01-01' AND completion_status = 'Complete';
SELECT intervention_type, COUNT(*) AS total_evaluations FROM Evaluation GROUP BY intervention_type;
SELECT student_name, intervention_type, effectiveness_rating FROM Evaluation ORDER BY effectiveness_rating DESC;
SELECT * FROM Evaluation WHERE effectiveness_rating > 3;
SELECT student_name, effectiveness_rating FROM Evaluation WHERE intervention_type = 'Therapy';
SELECT program_name, start_date, end_date FROM ProgramData WHERE completion_status = 'Complete';
SELECT * FROM Evaluation WHERE intervention_type = 'Behavioral' AND effectiveness_rating >= 4;
SELECT student_name, intervention_type, effectiveness_rating FROM Evaluation WHERE intervention_type = 'Counseling' ORDER BY effectiveness_rating DESC;
SELECT * FROM interventions WHERE intervention_type = 'Therapy' ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT intervention_name, start_date, end_date FROM interventions WHERE intervention_type = 'Meditation' ORDER BY start_date ASC;
SELECT intervention_name, intervention_type, start_date FROM interventions WHERE start_date > '2022-01-01' AND end_date < '2030-12-31';
SELECT first_name, last_name, age, gender FROM participants WHERE age > 30 AND gender = 'Female';
SELECT participant_id, effectiveness_score, feedback FROM intervention_results WHERE effectiveness_score >= 80 ORDER BY effectiveness_score DESC, participant_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM interventions ORDER BY start_date DESC, intervention_name LIMIT 10;
SELECT first_name, last_name, age FROM participants WHERE gender = 'Female';
SELECT intervention_name, start_date, end_date, COUNT(*) FROM interventions GROUP BY intervention_name, start_date, end_date HAVING COUNT(*) > 1 ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC;

SELECT p.first_name, p.last_name, i.intervention_name, ir.effectiveness_score FROM participants p JOIN intervention_results ir ON p.participant_id = ir.participant_id JOIN interventions i ON i.intervention_id = ir.intervention_id WHERE ir.effectiveness_score > 80 ORDER BY ir.effectiveness_score DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM intervention_results WHERE feedback IS NOT NULL ORDER BY result_id ASC LIMIT 20;
SELECT * FROM Students;
SELECT student_name, grade_level FROM Students ORDER BY grade_level DESC;
SELECT course_name, instructor_id FROM Courses WHERE course_name LIKE 'Math%';
SELECT student_name, enrollment_date FROM Students WHERE grade_level = 10 ORDER BY enrollment_date ASC;
SELECT student_name, intervention_type FROM Students JOIN Interventions ON Students.student_id = Interventions.student_id WHERE intervention_type = 'Tutoring';
SELECT * FROM Students ORDER BY student_name DESC, enrollment_date ASC;
SELECT student_name, grade_level FROM Students WHERE grade_level > 10;
SELECT course_name, course_description FROM Courses WHERE instructor_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT student_name, course_name FROM Students JOIN Enrollments ON Students.student_id = Enrollments.student_id JOIN Courses ON Courses.course_id = Enrollments.course_id;

SELECT student_name, intervention_type, intervention_date FROM Students JOIN Interventions ON Students.student_id = Interventions.student_id WHERE intervention_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY intervention_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM Students
SELECT student_id, student_name, age FROM Students
SELECT course_name, instructor_id, credit_hours FROM Courses
SELECT student_id, course_id, enrollment_date, grade FROM Enrollments
SELECT instructor_name, email FROM Instructors
SELECT student_name, age, gender FROM Students WHERE age >= 18;
SELECT course_name, department, credit_hours FROM Courses WHERE credit_hours > 3;
SELECT instructor_name, experience_years, email FROM Instructors WHERE department = 'Mathematics';
SELECT student_name, grade FROM Students s JOIN Enrollments e ON s.student_id = e.student_id WHERE e.grade = 'A';
SELECT course_name, instructor_name, department FROM Courses c JOIN Instructors i ON c.instructor_id = i.instructor_id WHERE department = 'Science';
